name: Katowice 2019-seerpas
description: This is a sealed IEM 2019 Katowice CS:GO Major Championship viewer pass. You can redeem a Souvenir Package every time you upgrade your Coin.

name: Berlin 2019-seerpas
description: Dette er et forseglet seerpas til StarLadder 2019 Berlin CS:GO Major-mesterskabet. Optjen en souvenirpolet, hver gang du opgraderer mønten.
